01:28:02,921 --> 01:28:10,121
Oh, if Samson have only been in this meeting here before everything started to crumble.


1053
01:28:12,361 --> 01:28:13,721
If you're standing


1054
01:28:13,721 --> 01:28:16,201
come out of your seat and just come up here.


1055
01:28:16,201 --> 01:28:19,481
You can stand, you can kneel


1056
01:28:19,481 --> 01:28:20,521
do what you want.


1057
01:28:21,801 --> 01:28:23,321
I give you my word


1058
01:28:23,321 --> 01:28:28,201
I and others will stay with you as long as you just want to quietly pray.


1059
01:28:28,201 --> 01:28:29,641
Come on, come out of your seat.


1060
01:28:52,201 --> 01:28:53,081
Then we'll pray.


1061
01:28:53,081 --> 01:28:54,441
But now we're going to sing.


1062
01:33:30,121 --> 01:33:31,241
We're coming home.


1063
01:33:31,241 --> 01:33:32,841
Forgive us.


1064
01:33:32,841 --> 01:33:35,481
Forgive us our trespasses, Lord.


1065
01:33:36,521 --> 01:33:40,521
As we forgive those who trespass against us, forgive us, Lord.


1066
01:33:42,041 --> 01:33:43,961
Wash away iniquity.


1067
01:33:45,081 --> 01:33:47,241
Have mercy on us, Lord.


1068
01:33:58,201 --> 01:34:00,521
There's mercy with you today, Lord.


1069
01:34:00,521 --> 01:34:01,641
You love us.


1070
01:34:01,641 --> 01:34:03,081
We're coming home.


1071
01:34:03,081 --> 01:34:04,281
What were we doing?


1072
01:34:05,481 --> 01:34:07,001
How long have we been?